# CSP adaptée à Youtubator — remplace celle du vhost websecurity (nethttp.net),
# trop stricte : elle bloquait l'IFrame API YouTube, les embeds, Google Sign-In
# et l'API YouTube Data. Inerte ailleurs (GitHub Pages ignore les .htaccess).
Header always unset Content-Security-Policy
Header always set Content-Security-Policy "default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' https://www.youtube.com https://s.ytimg.com https://accounts.google.com; frame-src https://www.youtube.com https://www.youtube-nocookie.com https://accounts.google.com; connect-src 'self' https://www.googleapis.com https://accounts.google.com https://www.youtube.com; img-src 'self' data: https://i.ytimg.com https://*.ggpht.com https://*.googleusercontent.com; media-src 'self' blob:; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://accounts.google.com; font-src 'self'; frame-ancestors 'self'"
